had enabled Thomson-CSF to keep its turnover steady last year at FFr34bn.
The French government this week confirmed its decision to renew Mr Gomez's
tenure as president of Thomson SA, the group holding company, as well as of
Thomson-CSF.
Thomson SA had an overall net loss last year of FFr3.03bn, largely due to
Thomson-CSF's FFr2.3bn net loss.
