by way of a management buy-out, the terms of which were revealed by
Waterhouse yesterday.
The value of the net assets being disposed of amounts to Pounds 64,948. The
proceeds of the sale, which is subject to shareholders' approval, will be
used to reduce indebtedness and to provide working capital.
