FT  07 JUL 94 / People: Santini posted at Mills &amp; Allen
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Musical chairs at Mills &amp; Allen, one of the UK's leading outdoor media -
poster - groups, a subsidiary of the French advertising and media group
Avenir Havas Media.
