Il Manifesto managed: 'Forza Buddha' (Let's Go Buddha) referring to Baggio's
religion.
Celebrations were marred in Naples where Salvatore Oliva, 7, was
accidentally killed when his 15-year-old cousin fired his father's pistol to
celebrate, news reports said. The cousin was charged with manslaughter.
