</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P6531 Real Estate Agents and Managers.
    P7513 Truck Rental and Leasing, No Drivers.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>CMMT  Comment &amp; Analysis.
    FIN  Annual report.
