FT  06 JUL 94 / Observer: Dog of war
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
On the Pacific island of Guam - at the US official war dog cemetery - you
will soon be able to visit a life-size bronze sculpture of a Doberman,
erected in honour of the many dogs which died helping US troops in the war
against Japan.
